lead_paragraph: Another professional fighter landed a victory at the Rio Games on Sunday, a second day of Olympic boxing that also featured one lightweight arguing outside the ring that organizers had conspired against him.

headline.print_headline: Boxing: Second Professional Advances on Day Two of Rio Games
